reviewText: It says it comes with English subtitles and mine did not. I have read several books on the Miracle of Guadalupe and I am going to keep the movie only because I have read enough to follow the story from the books I have read but the movie was a disappointment. Saying it has English subtitles and then not having them is a big deal to me.
